Day and World War II at large and their 2023 return to the beaches of Normandy, where they reminisce on the unprecedented operation and are celebrated by the local French citizens of the seaside region.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.988551805176914, \"rank\": 0.00608082731577535, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The piece documents\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"veterans\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"D-Day and World War II\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"the beaches\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"Normandy\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"the unprecedented operation\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"the seaside region\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Known as the operation that began the liberation of France and, ultimately, laid the groundwork for the demise of the Axis powers, D-Day is, arguably, one of the most pivotal days in 20thcentury global history.\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 891, \"end\": 897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9784683415447296, \"rank\": 0.01994805197971052, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the operation\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"the liberation\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"the groundwork\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"the demise\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"the Axis powers\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"D-Day\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"the most pivotal days\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"20thcentury global history\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In these 22 minutes, viewers get access to the soldiers who were on the frontlines of this historic day - and how 80 years later, their heroic actions are still felt around the world and particularly in northern France.\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1262, \"end\": 1268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9784683415447296, \"rank\": 0.01994805197971052, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these 22 minutes\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"the soldiers\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"the frontlines\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"this historic day\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"their heroic actions\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The story of the young American men and women who served so valiantly alongside the other Allied Forces 80 years ago is one that should never be lost to time and history,\\\" saidRon Vaccaro, VP, Editorial at NBC Sports.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1295, \"end\": 1303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999710117440183, \"rank\": 2.8988801932814192e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1362, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allies_of_World_War_II\", \"score\": 0.9999999640